## Add Features

Add features with the ibl.ai skills -- each creates the files and wires them in:

- `/iblai-auth` — SSO authentication + Redux store + providers
- `/iblai-agent-chat` — in-process agent chat surface
- `/iblai-profile` — user profile dropdown
- `/iblai-notification` — notification bell with unread badge
- `/iblai-ops-build` — Tauri v2 desktop/mobile shell

(Ensure the `@iblai/mcp` server + skills are configured in `.mcp.json`.)

